urlText: L2 and L3 Lines - Moore Park lift out of service
content:
The lift at Moore Park light rail stop (Anzac Parade side of the Dr Agnes Bennett footbridge) on the L2 Randwick Line and L3 Kingsford Line is temporarily out of service until further notice.

For your safety, do not use even if the doors open.

Alternative access:
  • Use the stairs if able to
  • Or use the accessible entry/exit pathway via the crossing at the intersection of Anzac Parade and Lang Rd.
     
For urgent assistance:
Use the Help Point if on the platform
Or call 131 500
